<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7187841>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Pictures of relevant Troyus species:A) sequenced Troyus phyllides from Suriname (molecular voucher: 19022E04; deposited in USNM); B) genitalia of Troyus phyllides from Rondônia, Brazil (dissection vial: SN-20-107; deposited in MGCL); C) Lectotype of Papilio marcus Fabricius, 1787 housed in ZMUC (ZMUC 00029699); D) Lectotype of Vettius phyllides housed at SMT (molecular voucher: 18094F06)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7187841/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7187843>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. The earliest recorded illustrations of “marcus” (placed in the genus Cobalus) in Geyer (1832). From the Ernst Mayr Library and Archives of the Museum of Comparative Zoology, Harvard University." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7187843/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

